    <!--
	Live List specification
	    - Dynamic: Create frames as necessary
	    - Customizable: Change sizes (width, font size)
	    - Uses No cpu if nothing to do
	    - Simple API
	    - Maintain an array with current Debuffs shown
	    - When someone is debuffed, check for range changes
	    - Shares MUFs ressources: uses the work done by the MUFs API if the MUFs are displayed
		- Especially for in range checks
		- Will also uses Debuffs found

	Suggested APIs:

	- :AddToLiveList( Unit, Debuff ) where Debuff is a Debuff table as used in Decursive
	    - this function may also find the priority of the unit
	- :DelayedAddToLivelist ( Unit, Debuff )
	Object:SetDebuff(Unit, Debuff)

	Static public properties:
	.UnitShown : the number of unit currently displayed
	.LiveListFull : Boolean, true if no more unit can be added (avoid a function call)

	Others:
	- Priority system:
	    - Position in the unit array
	    - X 100 if the unit is charmed

	TODO:
	- Add a message if the user cliks on the Live-List to cure...

    -->



